## Markdown

Markdown provides a shorthand means of generating HTML.  It is used for the content of guides, as well as some facets
 of code annotation.

*References*

<a href="https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet" target="_blank">https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Cheatsheet</a>

## Guides

Guides are stored under the root directory under contents/guides.

##API Documentation

API Documentation will be generated into a docs directory under the project root via these tasks.

    > grunt dev
or

    > grunt serve
